# Summary
The Personas chart in Amplitude groups users into clusters based on event behavior similarities, enabling exploratory data mining to discover user personas without pre-specified rules. Available only on Growth and Enterprise plans, it uses a unique interface with Cluster Generation, Cluster Count, and Target Cohort modules instead of the standard Amplitude chart components.

